#: config.inc.php:78
#, php-format
msgid "Test email to %s"
msgstr "Pošlji testno sporočilo na %s"

#: config.inc.php:80
msgid "This is a test email generated by the Email SMTP RosarioSIS plugin."
msgstr "To je testno sporočilo programa Metis."

#: config.inc.php:142
#, php-format
msgid "Email SMTP %s"
msgstr "Email SMTP %s"

#: config.inc.php:149
msgid ""
"If you are sending using an email provider (Gmail, Yahoo, Hotmail, Outlook."
"com, etc) this setting should be your email address for this account."
msgstr ""
"V primeru da uporabljate (Gmail, Yahoo, Outlook.com in podobno) je  vaš "
"elektronski naslov vaše uporabniško ime."

#: config.inc.php:156
msgid "From Email"
msgstr "Sporočilo od"

#: config.inc.php:163
#, php-format
msgid ""
"You can specify the name that emails should be sent from. If you leave this "
"blank, the emails will be sent from %s."
msgstr ""
"Določite lahko ime, iz katerega naj se pošiljajo e-poštna sporočila. Če "
"pustite to polje prazno, bodo e-poštna sporočila poslana iz %s."

#: config.inc.php:170
msgid "From Name"
msgstr ""

#: config.inc.php:179
msgid "SMTP Host"
msgstr ""

#: config.inc.php:188
msgid "SMTP Port"
msgstr ""

#: config.inc.php:202
msgid "Encryption"
msgstr "Enkripcija"

#: config.inc.php:229
msgid ""
"If you are sending more than 50 emails at once and receive an SMTP error, "
"adding a pause between each email may help."
msgstr ""
"Če pošiljate več kot 50 e-poštnih sporočil hkrati in prejmete napako SMTP, "
"vam bo morda pomagalo dodati premor med posameznimi e-poštnimi sporočili."

#: config.inc.php:236
msgid "Pause between each email (seconds)"
msgstr "Premor med vsakim e-poštnim sporočilom (sekunde)"

#: config.inc.php:244
msgid "Send a test email To"
msgstr "Pošlji testno e-poštno sporočilo na"

#: config.inc.php:247
msgid "Send Test"
msgstr "Pošlji test"

